---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description="OutMore Adventures privacy policy. How we collect, use, and protect your information."
>
  <section class="py-20 sm:py-24 bg-valley-cream">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h1 class="mb-4">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-granite-mid text-sm mb-12">Last updated: March 2026</p>

      <div class="space-y-8 text-granite-mid leading-relaxed">
        <div>
          <h2 class="mb-4">Information We Collect</h2>
          <p>
            When you book an experience or contact us through our website, we may collect personal information
            including your name, email address, phone number, and payment information. Payment processing is
            handled securely through our booking partner, FlyBook.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="mb-4">How We Use Your Information</h2>
          <p>We use your personal information to:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 mt-3">
            <li>Process and confirm your bookings</li>
            <li>Communicate with you about your experience (pickup times, what to bring, etc.)</li>
            <li>Send you the Yosemite Journal newsletter, if you've subscribed</li>
            <li>Respond to your inquiries and provide customer support</li>
            <li>Improve our services and website</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="mb-4">Third-Party Services</h2>
          <p>
            We use FlyBook for booking and payment processing. When you make a reservation, your payment
            information is handled directly by FlyBook under their own privacy policy. We do not store
            credit card information on our servers.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="mb-4">Cookies and Analytics</h2>
          <p>
            We use privacy-friendly analytics to understand how visitors use our website. We do not use
            tracking cookies or share your browsing data with advertisers.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="mb-4">Your Rights</h2>
          <p>
            You may request access to, correction of, or deletion of your personal information at any time
            by contacting us at <a href="mailto:hello@outmoreadventures.com" class="text-sequoia hover:underline">hello@outmoreadventures.com</a>.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="mb-4">Contact</h2>
          <p>
            If you have questions about this privacy policy, please contact us at
            <a href="mailto:hello@outmoreadventures.com" class="text-sequoia hover:underline">hello@outmoreadventures.com</a>.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
